Lang5 cho3 phaiN2 be7-bian2-tit siu7 heng5-hoat8. Chit-si3 au7-si3 long2 si7 an2-ni. Chai7-seN i-e5 sim be7 peng5-an, u7 sit-loh8 the2-bian7, iah8 hou7 lang5 pan7-choe7.  Si2-au7 heng5-hoat8 si7 kek8-tang7 kek8-tng5; iah8 be7 siam2-pi7--tit.
Lang5 cho3 ho2 kim-si3 siu7 sian7-po3, u7 tit-tioh8 an-sim koh hou7 lang5 tui3-tiong7, iah8 koe3-si3 hiong2-siu7 eng2-oan2 e5 toa7 eng5-kng, koh tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 bu5-han7 e5 siuN2-su3.
Cheng3-lang5 tioh8 kin2-sin7 boh8-tit cho3-khi2-thau5 sio2-khoa2 e5 phaiN2, kiaN-liau2 hit-e5 phaiN2-iuN7 si7 na2-ku2 na2-toa7, chiu7 heng5-hoat8 si7 na2-ku2 na2-tang7.  Lan2 tai7-ke tioh8 siong5-siong5 kiu5 Siong7-te3 hou7 goan2 kau3-giah8 ti3-sek kiam khui3-lat8 lai5 thoat-li7 tak8-hang7 e5 choe7-ok.
Ti7 e7-te2 u7 ki3-chai3 nng7-chat-su7 lai5 piau2-beng5 ok iu2 ok-po3, iah8 keng2-kai3 lang5 tioh8 ti5-hong5 boh8-tit hoan7-choe7. Chong2-si7 lang5 m7-thang phah-sng3 e7-bin7 ki3-chai3 chan5-jim2 e5 heng5-hoat8 si7 hap8-gi5.
Sio-si2 kiap-koan e5 lang5
Bun5-beng5-hiaN u7 hoe5-phoe thong-ti Chap8-saN-kah kau3-hoe7 lang5 e5 khiam3-khoeh chiu7 soa3 sia2 chit8-hang7, chiu7-si7 Sio-si2 kiap-koan e5 lang5. Phoe u7 kong2:
Koh-chit8-hang7 e5 tai7-chi3, si7 goa2 sou2 m7-bat khoaN3-tioh8 e5 su7, chiu7-si7 lang5 oah8-oah8 ka7-i sio-si2.  Chiu7-si7 tu2-tioh8 ku7-ni5 chit-ho7 e5 ni5-tang, bo5-thang-chiah8, che7-che7 cho3-chhat8 e5 lang5 thau koah-beh8, thau liu2 han5-chu5; goa2 sou2 kong2 hou7 lang5 sio-si2 hit-e5 lang5, si7 ui7-tioh8 me5--si5 khi3 kiap-koan, ia7 hou7 lang5 liah8--tioh8, in-ui7 hit-e5 lang5 chin-gau5 kiap lang5 e5 bong7.  Chiau3 chia e5 se3-siok8-lang5 kong2, hit e5 lang5 kiap lang5 e5 bong7 chin-gau5, in-ui7 lang5 e5 bong7 chap8-hun7 chha-put-to hou7 i kiap si3-hun7 khi3.
Kau3 ti7 ji7-goeh8-chhe iu5-goan5 si7 chhut mng5 khi3 kiap-bong7, hit-me5-hng tu2-gu7 hiah e5 teh-chiu2 han5-chu5, chiu2 chhai3-thau5 e5 lang5, chiu7 hou7 in liah8-tioh8, koaiN-teh, kau3 ti7 chit ji7-goeh8 ji7-it chia e5 chong2-li2 lau7-toa7 chiah gi2 kong2 tioh8 ka7-i sio-si2-khi3, bian2-tit hou7-i oah8-teh lai5 sng2-hoai7 lang5 e5 hong-sui2, chiu7 ti7 hit ji7-it-jit8 chha-put-to chap8-ji7-tiam2-chhut e5 si5 chhoa7-khi3 Pou-sim lam5-peng5 hit e5 pou, ti7-hia chhai7-thiau7, pak8 hit-e5 lang5 ti7 thiau7--nih8, si3-ui5 chiah chiong tek-chhi3-oe kap tek-khou lai5 chiap ti7 hit-e5 lang5 e5 seng-khu, lau5 i e5 heng5-kham2 kap thau5-khak chhut-hian7, e7-te2 chiah chiong chhau2-a2 lai5 in2-hoe2.
Kau3 teh-beh pang3-hoe2 sio e5 si5, goa2 chau2-khi3 Pou-sim-ke, in-ui7 m7-kaN2 khoaN3 hit-e5 lang5 ti7 hoe2 e5 tiong-ng, ia7 m7-kaN2 thiaN i ti7 hoe2 tiong-ng ai-kio3 e5 siaN2.  Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 hit-e5 lang5 chin the3 i kan-khou2, kau3 beh lau5-bak8-sai2 chhut-lai5.  Hit-e5 lang5 goa2 khoaN3 long2 bo5 hoan5-lo2 e5 khoan2-sit.  Goa2 thiaN-kiN3 hiaN-ti7 teh kong2, hoe2 i2-keng khi2-toh8 chin-iam7, sio-tioh8 i e5 saN-a2-khou3 e5 si5, i-e5 chhui3 iau2 teh pou7 pin5-nng5, iah8-bo5 ai3-kio3; kau3 hit-tiap8 thau5-mng5 i2-keng hou7 hoe2 sio-khi3, seng-khu ia7 hou7 hoe2 sio-tioh8, chha-put-to beh tng7-khui3 e5 si5, kong2 chiah u7 io5-thau5 haiN7 saN-siaN chiah si2.  
Hit-e5 lang5 tu2-tioh8 sio e5 khoan2 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 Thian-lou7-lek8-theng5.  Chin7-tiong ti7 Hu-hoa-chhi7 hou7 lang5 sio e5 khoan2-sit chhai7 chit8-ki-thiau7, eng7 thih-soaN3 lai5 pak8 i-e5 seng-khu ti7 thiau7--nih8.  Lun7 teh khoaN3 e5 lang5 si7 chha-put-to chhin-chhiuN7 Hi-pek-lai5 e5 phoe 12:1 sou2 kong2, ‘KhoaN3 e5 lang5 hiah-choe7, chhin-chhiuN7 hun5 teh taN3’, hit e5 thiong2-pou long2-si7 lang5.  Hit-si5 lang5 sio-si2 liau2, lang5 chiu7 phoa3 i-e5 pak-tou2 lai5 theh8 i-e5 sim-koaN, kong2 si7 beh khi3 chiah8, HaiN7 ah, thai3 u7 hiah chan5-jim2 e5 lang5 ah! Sio-si2 to siuN-khek-khui lah, iu7-koh lai5 chiah8 i-e5 seng-khu ah!  
TaN sou2 kong2 si7 chiah-e5: kiu5 sian-seN the3 goan2 ki5-to2, hou7 chiah e5 hiaN-ti7 e7-tit-thang chai au7-lai5 e5 heng5-hoat8 chhin-chhiuN7 hit-ho7; chiu7 bian2-tit kou-hu7 Chu2 e5 chhim-in, e7-tit-thang siam2-pi7 au7-lai5 e5 heng5-hoat8; iah8 the3 goa2 ki5-to2 hou7 goa2 e7-tit-thang gau5 li7-ek chiah hiaN-ti7 chi2-moe7.  Si7 sim-sou2-goan7.  
Gin2-a2 cho3 toa7-chhat8 hou7 koaN-hu2 ou2 bak8-chiu
Siok8-gu2 kong2, ‘Giam5 koaN-hu2 chhut kau7-chhat8.’  In-ui7 cheng5-goeh8 Hong7-soaN-koan7-siok8 e5 kui2-na7 sou2-chai7 hou7 chhat8 cheng-piang3, Koan7-chu2 Li2 kam3 u7 khi2 tui7-ngou2 khi3 A-li2-kang2 kin7-hu7 e5 chng-siu7 ui5 chhat8-chng.  Chhat8 long2 thoat-li7, u7 chhiau-tioh8 kui2-na7 pou3-te7 mih8; u7-e5 chin tat8-chiN5, chiu7-si7 u7-giah8-lang5 e5 saN-a2-kun5, chit8-hu3 tat8-tit saN-si3-chap8 gin5.  Koan7-chu2 long2 m7-chun2 ge5-iah8 tham-sim hia e5 mih8, i long2 u7 tak8-hang7 koe3-tiam2 kau hiah-e5 pan-thau5 khoaN3 si7 sim2-mih8 lang5 hou7 chhat8 chhiuN2--e5, kio3 lang5 khi3 jin7, jin7 na7 si7 i-e5, i thang theh8 to3--khi3.  Pan-thau5 chin7-chiong hiah e5 mih8-kiaN7 tiau3 ti7 bio7-khau2 chhin-chhiuN7 kou2-i-tiam3 e5 khoan2-sit.  
Hian7-chai7 chit-e5 Hong7-soaN-koan7 put-chi2 chheng-liam5; ia7 chin gau5 liah8 chhat8, tui3 i chiuN7-jim7 si3-gou7-ni5, liah8 chha-put-to si3-gou7-chap8 e5 cheng-piang3 chhat8 lai5 thai5-thau5.  Chong2-si7 cheng-piang3 chhat8 e5 tiong-kan ia7 u7 chap8-si3-gou7 hoe3 e5 gin2-na2.   Kin7-lai5 u7 liah8-tioh8 chit8-e5 15 hoe3 e5 toa7-chhat8.  Koan7-chu2 kong2 be7 pan7-tit thai5-thau5, u7 chiong nng7-lui2 bak8-chiu phah-chhut-lai5, au7-lai5 siu7 kaN, theng3-hau7 bak8-chiu the3-hong5, chiu7 beh phai3 chhe-iah8, chhoa7 i khi3 i cheng-piang3 e5 sou2-chai7 phah-lo5 iu5-ke, soa3 kong2-khi2 i cho3 chhat8 e5 cheng5-iu5 hou7 lang5 chai.
(Tai5-lam5 Hu2-siaN5 Kau3-hoe7-po3 te7 98 koan3, 1893 ni5 6 geh8) 
